Well - mostly when we'd finished. Of course - you see - us big ones used to have to help the little ones. And see that they finished all theirs up. And then when - they'd ea
ten the - the vegetables and that kind of thing of course all the plates was taken out into the kitchen, and the pudding brought in you see, because we - we all had to do that.
