Well I think he did once. But - of course he was a man as had - like me had got strong - strong views and you stood up for what he - what he - what he thought. And it - and - of course
 he'd never worked anywhere else, only Fletcher's. As - but - they were more or less - more like - they wasn't like - employers, you know, they were - they could talk to one another.
