None. He hadn't time. Because you see - you get up to go to work at four o'clock in the morning you want some bed don't you. That's - no - mm. That's right. No. They didn't have time. No. Mind you, he - he used to - be very fond of gardening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8148024 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322814\charrsid354 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
