No. Because you see she used to make all our own clothes. She even made the boys suits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8148024 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322814\charrsid354 With twelve of you she'd be fully engaged in that wouldn't she?
