 to pay for it, to pay her, but that was all. A doctor - used to come every fortnight, doctor's man used to come every fortnight, I know that. You'd always a bill, doctors bill, and there was a lot of you, and she used to pay so much every fortnight. Same
 
with the coalman. Name was Allyn. Wright and Allyn I can remember that. One was a big man, the other was a great big man, six foot - and - winter and summer she used to pay - this amount - to these - to them, and that kept us in coal you see. We were neve
r short of a fire, never. And we're never short of anything if it come to that, mind you, although - I say it, I mean we'd always - good clothes, and good food if it was - if it was rough it was good.
