 I left school when I was twelve. And - there was a new baby born then, I can quite remember that. But they - the midwife used to come. And I - had to look after - the other children and I did the cooking. But I didn't do the washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8148024 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322814\charrsid354 Were there any of your parents relatives living nearby?
