y they were - meet when they were going shopping and that kind of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8148024 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16322814\charrsid354 Did your mother and father share the same friends, as a couple?
